'''Atom'''是由[[GitHub|GitHub]]開發的[[自由及开放源代码软件|自由及开放源代码]]的[[文字編輯器|文字與程式碼編輯器]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.techspot.com/news/55845-github-unveils-atom-text-editor-for-developers.html |title=Github unveils Atom text editor for developers |date=2014-02-28 |publisher=techspot |accessdate=2014-05-07 |archive-date=2014-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140508030524/http://www.techspot.com/news/55845-github-unveils-atom-text-editor-for-developers.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://wwwhatsnew.com/2014/05/06/github-presenta-su-editor-atom-ahora-open-source/ |title=El editor para programadores, Atom, de GitHub, ahora es de código libre |publisher=wwwhatsnew |accessdate=2014-05-07 |archive-date=2014-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140508031035/http://wwwhatsnew.com/2014/05/06/github-presenta-su-editor-atom-ahora-open-source/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，支持[[macOS|macOS]]、[[Windows|Windows]]和[[Linux|Linux]]作業系統<ref>{{Cite web |title=Atom FAQ |url=https://atom.io/faq |accessdate=2014-08-09 |archive-date=2014-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626154027/https://atom.io/faq |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，支援[[Node.js|Node.js]]所寫的外掛程式<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.javaworld.com/article/2151781/html-css-js/github-releases-free-and-open-atom-code-editor.html |title=GitHub releases free and open Atom code editor |date=2014-05-06 |publisher=javaworld |accessdate=2014-05-07 |archive-date=2014-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140508025004/http://www.javaworld.com/article/2151781/html-css-js/github-releases-free-and-open-atom-code-editor.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並內建由[[GitHub|Github]]提供的[[Git|Git版本控制系統]]。多數的延伸套件皆為開放原始碼授權，並由社群建置與維護<ref>{{Cite web |title=Atom Packages |url=https://atom.io/packages |accessdate=2014-05-06 |archive-date=2014-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701062707/https://atom.io/packages |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Atom基於使用[[Chromium|Chromium]]和Node.js的跨平台应用框架[[Electron|Electron]]（最初名为Atom Shell），并使用[[CoffeeScript|CoffeeScript]]和[[LESS_(层叠样式表)|Less]]撰寫<ref>{{Cite web |title="The Nucleus of Atom" |url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atom_(text_editor) |author=Official Atom Blog |accessdate=2014-05-06 |archive-date=2014-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324075402/http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atom_(text_editor) |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Atom也可當作[[整合開發環境|IDE]]使用<ref name="nuclide">{{Cite web |title=Nuclide |url=https://nuclide.io/ |accessdate=2016-10-12 |website=Nuclide |archive-date=2016-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013083656/https://nuclide.io/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="juno">{{Cite web |title=Juno, the Interactive Development Environment |url=http://junolab.org/ |accessdate=2016-10-12 |website=Juno |archive-date=2016-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010090052/http://junolab.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="platformio">{{Cite web |title=PlatformIO IDE: The next-generation integrated development environment for IoT |url=http://platformio.org/platformio-ide |accessdate=2016-10-12 |dead-url=yes |website=PlatformIO |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013145638/http://platformio.org/platformio-ide |archive-date=2016-10-13 }}</ref>。被它的开发者称为“21 世纪的“高自訂性”文本编辑器（hackable text editor for the 21st Century）”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://atom.io/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-05-06 |archive-date=2014-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140605043122/https://atom.io/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>自2014年5月6日起，Atom的核心程式、套件管理器以及Atom基於Chromium的桌面程式框架皆使用[[MIT授權條款|MIT授權條款]]釋出<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://techcrunch.com/2014/05/06/github-open-sources-its-atom-text-editor/ |title=GitHub Open Sources Its Atom Text Editor |publisher=TechCrunch |accessdate=2014-05-07 |archive-date=2014-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140507163250/http://techcrunch.com/2014/05/06/github-open-sources-its-atom-text-editor/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Atom Is Now Open Source |url=http://blog.atom.io/2014/05/06/atom-is-now-open-source.html |accessdate=2015-09-06 |archive-date=2017-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170424022832/http://blog.atom.io/2014/05/06/atom-is-now-open-source.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

在2022年6月8号，[[GitHub|GitHub]]正式宣布在2022年12月15日关闭Atom，并存档其存储库<ref>{{cite web |author1=GitHub Staff |title=Sunsetting Atom |url=https://github.blog/2022-06-08-sunsetting-atom/ |accessdate=2022-06-09 |date=2022-06-08}}</ref>。

